	To make GDM start at boot with systemd, run:\n
	# systemctl enable gdm.service\n
	\n
	To make GDM start at boot with OpenRC, edit /etc/conf.d to have
	DISPLAYMANAGER=\"gdm\" and enable the xdm service:\n
	# rc-update add xdm
